description:
&lt;p&gt;Would you like to join our award winning Hospital at Home Service?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently looking for 2X full time Band 6 nurses to join our busy, dynamic team based at Kent and Canterbury Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you forward thinking, a team player and able to work autonomously visiting patient&#39;s in the home environment delivering gold standard, holistic care?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you proactive and invested into working with different disciplines in East Kent to create unique pathways to ensure inpatient hospital treatment can be implemented at home?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team is friendly, unique and is looking for the right individual to join us. You will be based at Kent and Canterbury Hospital however on occasions you will be required to cover our sister teams at either WHH in Ashford or the QEQM team in Margate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameLisa DentJob titleWard ManagerEmail addressldent1@nhs.netTelephone number07825703799Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details please contact&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lisa Dent, Ward Manager QEQM/KCH at ldent1@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tiffany Carnegie, Ward Manager WHH at tiffanycarnegie @nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
